The commands with which we can send slack message with file attachment

for example:

tcctl slack file_upload \
    --channel "#devops" \
    --message "This is the message with file attachment" \
    --file "/tmp/filename"

where:

channel            - (required variable) the name of Slack channel
message            - (required variable) the Slack message body
file               - (required variable) the path for file which will be attach into message
